data.description: Great Neighborhood off the interstate (hwy 281) between University and Sprague. This spacious home is open and inviting with a large master suite with glass office door office area. The garage has been converted into an exercise/play/media room. There is a 2-vehicle carport and the house has an oversized corner lot that faces west. The covered patio area is great for BBQ and there's a side entrance for when vehicles need to be stored off the street. The location is very close to many parks, shopping, UTRGV, and the Bert Ogden arena! Reach out to listing agent to discuss solar panels. Call now to book your private showing. This gem won't last long.
